{"tid":838561,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［窮撚美食］大快活早餐一餐兩食","createTime":"2018-09-27T08:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T15:03:21.000Z","uid":44828,"like":5,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e08386c401a2417a28d60eab22bf005902bd85f","tid":838561,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:12:29.000Z","msg":"小弟做緊廢青 每日都用50蚊食早午餐<br />\n一般早餐一個唐包加咖啡 <br />\n午餐就排骨飯或者燒味<br />\n大概就40蚊左右<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢期留意到大快活有個C03餐 $43個半<br />\n有雞扒炒蛋方包同埋腿通<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早餐先食個方包同半舊雞扒 半隻蛋<br />\n晏就食埋火腿通粉 夠晒飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔洗日日食包食飯咁悶，仲可以揸下刀切切下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/161156_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F161156_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ce53516e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b802a8ebbb877675f715685417a1d0cd23d85ccf","tid":838561,"uid":76098,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"大快活學生餐31~35蚊不等, 有腸扒飯,肉意,咕嚕肉飯<br />\nshow一show學生證就得, 唔會check <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6daaebf7570ac8d59e960ead36a02a6c6953855","tid":838561,"uid":67028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:26:36.000Z","msg":"去是旦一間茶記都食到 仲可以平d"},{"pid":"f56580fb934a4b9b3c44735f5abf218cd8f1eea1","tid":838561,"uid":49974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:27:12.000Z","msg":"原來出街食早餐已經要上到四字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52bd6ba488d81dc81507c5a816547a9fa56866fc","tid":838561,"uid":23011,"like":0,"disli